<h1 id='custom-perk-redemptions-by-user'>Custom Perk Redemptions By User</h1><h2 id='get-get-all-custom-perk-redemptions-for-a-user'>[GET] Get All Custom Perk Redemptions for a User</h2><pre class="highlight shell tab-shell"><code>curl <span class="s2">"http://portify-api.herokuapp.com/companies/:company_id/admins/:admin_id/users/:user_id/custom_perk_redemptions"</span>
  -H <span class="s2">"Authorization"</span>: <span class="s2">"Token token=yourtoken"</span>
</code></pre>
