<p>This endpoint retrieves all custom perk redemptions for a specific user.</p>
<h3 id='url-parameters'>URL Parameters</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>company_id</td>
<td>The ID of your company</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>admin_id</td>
<td>The ID of your admin account</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>user_id</td>
<td>The ID of the user</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
